    <title>Linux common commands</title>
    <url>/2021/09/13/Linux-common-commands/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>紀錄 Linux 常用指令</p>
<span id="more"></span>

<h2 id="基本"><a href="#基本" class="headerlink" title="基本"></a>基本</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Command</th>
<th align="center">Name</th>
<th align="left">Documentation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">date</td>
<td align="center">Date</td>
<td align="left">查看日期</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">cal</td>
<td align="center">Calendar</td>
<td align="left">列出日曆</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">grep</td>
<td align="center">Globally search for a regular expression and print matching lines</td>
<td align="left">搜尋某些特定字元</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="網路功能"><a href="#網路功能" class="headerlink" title="網路功能"></a>網路功能</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Command</th>
<th align="center">Name</th>
<th align="left">Documentation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">ifconfig</td>
<td align="center">Interface configuration</td>
<td align="left">查詢目前系統的網路卡狀況</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">ping</td>
<td align="center">Ping</td>
<td align="left">查看對方網路是否有動作</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">hostname</td>
<td align="center">Hostname</td>
<td align="left">查看主機名稱</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">nslookup</td>
<td align="center">From name server lookup</td>
<td align="left">查詢或反查詢 DNS</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="系統管理員"><a href="#系統管理員" class="headerlink" title="系統管理員"></a>系統管理員</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Command</th>
<th align="center">Name</th>
<th align="left">Documentation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">top</td>
<td align="center">Table of processes</td>
<td align="left">列出目前系統的服務項目的動態資料</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">free</td>
<td align="center">Free</td>
<td align="left">查看記憶體</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">passwd</td>
<td align="center">Password</td>
<td align="left">改變密碼</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">clear</td>
<td align="center">Clear</td>
<td align="left">清除螢幕畫面</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="檔案與目錄管理"><a href="#檔案與目錄管理" class="headerlink" title="檔案與目錄管理"></a>檔案與目錄管理</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Command</th>
<th align="center">Name</th>
<th align="left">Documentation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">ls</td>
<td align="center">List</td>
<td align="left">列出目錄內之檔案與子目錄</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">cd</td>
<td align="center">Change directory</td>
<td align="left">改變目前目錄</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">pwd</td>
<td align="center">Print work directory</td>
<td align="left">列出目前所在路徑</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">cat</td>
<td align="center">Concatenate</td>
<td align="left">列出檔案內容</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">more</td>
<td align="center">More</td>
<td align="left">讀取更多內容(檔案太大時)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">mkdir</td>
<td align="center">Make directory</td>
<td align="left">建立目錄</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">rmdir</td>
<td align="center">Remove directory</td>
<td align="left">刪除目錄</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">rm</td>
<td align="center">Remove</td>
<td align="left">刪除檔案</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">cp</td>
<td align="center">Copy</td>
<td align="left">拷貝檔案</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">mv</td>
<td align="center">Move</td>
<td align="left">移動檔案或目錄</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">find</td>
<td align="center">Find</td>
<td align="left">列出尋找的檔案</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="登入與登出（開機與關機）"><a href="#登入與登出（開機與關機）" class="headerlink" title="登入與登出（開機與關機）"></a>登入與登出（開機與關機）</h2><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th align="left">Command</th>
<th align="center">Name</th>
<th align="left">Documentation</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td align="left">telnet</td>
<td align="center">Teletype network</td>
<td align="left">遠端登入</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">login</td>
<td align="center">Login</td>
<td align="left">登入系統</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">logout</td>
<td align="center">Logout</td>
<td align="left">離開作業系統</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">exit</td>
<td align="center">Exit</td>
<td align="left">離開 Linux 系統</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">shutdown</td>
<td align="center">Shutdown</td>
<td align="left">關機</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td align="left">reboot</td>
<td align="center">Reboot</td>
<td align="left">重新開機</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
]]></content>
